    "2": {
      "at": "2026-04-17T01:44:39.597Z",
      "feedback": "Add app/project version to the VERSION section of the card. Read from the project's package.json 'version' field (if present) or a VERSION file. Show it as a separate row: 'app v1.2.3'. If not found, row is absent. This is independent of aitri version — it shows what version of the product the team is building."
    },
    "ux": {
      "at": "2026-04-17T01:29:55.978Z",
      "feedback": "Remove expandable/collapsible detail section — all indicators must be visible without interaction. Reorganize card into 4 named sections: (1) BLOCKERS: drift, verify failed, phase rejection, critical/high bugs, blocking alerts count — only shown when issues exist; (2) PIPELINE: X/5 progress bar visual, current phase label, last pipeline event + age, last session agent+event+age; (3) QUALITY: test pass rate with progress bar, FR coverage count, spec quality warnings, compliance badge when available; (4) GIT: branch, last commit age, unpushed commits count (git rev-list @{u}..HEAD), uncommitted files count (git status --porcelain) — last two only shown when >0; (5) VERSION: aitri version of project, version mismatch warning if Hub vs installed differ. Health grade (A-F) stays in card header. Make visual wherever possible: progress bars for pipeline and tests, colored badges for status, icons per section. No velocity, no FR requirements summary table, no time-in-phase on card."
    }
  },
